<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.2.7">
<l>paḷḷi yālilai yēḻula kuṅkoḷḷum</l>
<l>vaḷḷal valva yiṟṟu perumā</l>
<l>ṉuḷḷu ḷāraṟi vāra vaṉṟaṉ</l>
<l>kaḷḷa māya maṉakka ruttē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>A banyan leaf as a bed, our lord with a strong stomach</l>
<l>that took the seven worlds, a liberal donor,</l>
<l>who will know in [their] minds the intention</l>
<l>of his deceptive, illusive mind?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
